{
  "stem": "7302.2",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they will fix it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There is a good man.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He-- he doesn't take too much.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They will fix you the watch.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So I went up till I find this place.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It wasn't easy for me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I didn't write much.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I didn't have money.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I didn't go nowhere.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Anyways, I found this place.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And-- and he told me, 'You come tomorrow.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You'll pick up your watch.' I was saying, 'I cannot come tomorrow.' [LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I didn't have money to-- to spend again for tickets, you know?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So he was saying, 'If you can wait an hour or two, I'll fix it for you.' So I was saying, 'I'll wait.' Meanwhile, I didn't have what to do.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I went up and down by the escalators.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "While I went up, I have seen a sign-- employment.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I was saying, 'What can I lose?'",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] I'll go in and ask.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Maybe they have a job for me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I went in.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I still, my-- my time wasn't saying--",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--I could read.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You know, when-- when you know other languages, you pick it up.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You-- you look at it, and you will know what this means.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But to write and to-- to say it, I couldn't.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] Anyways, they was having some Polish people working them.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So they was asking me what I want.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I told them if I could find a job.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And she was saying, 'You know, I think you are lucky.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Can you do something with a needle?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But it needs very fine work.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Of course, we have a department what they're selling the-- the leather gloves, the fine, very fine imported French kid gloves.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
